   2:../main.c     ****  * main.c - Morelle Falcon 15 EB BMS diagnostic over CAN
   3:../main.c     ****  *
   4:../main.c     ****  * Polls all BMS data IDs every 2 seconds and prints raw CAN bytes plus
   5:../main.c     ****  * decoded values via XMC_DEBUG (SWO / J-Link trace, view in DAVE Debug console).
   6:../main.c     ****  *
   7:../main.c     ****  * CAN: 250 kbps, extended 29-bit IDs, Node 0, P2.0 TX / P14.3 RX (RXDCB)
   8:../main.c     ****  */
